node.text:
Today we are stoked to talk about and put to the test @ericdressen’s ‘Rose Cross' Pro Model Deck! This shaped board was designed by Eric Dressen himself, & also features amazing artwork done by our friend @yaiagift. Be sure to stop by your local shop and see if they have this one available! We put Santa Cruz Skateboards Brand Manager @andrewcannon to the test with three NEW challenges to find out how this setup skates! Hit up our @youtube channel to watch now, then let us know in the comments below what challenges we should throw in the bins next!
👉 This week's product setup:
9.31x 31.94 Eric Dressen 'Rose Cross' Pro Model Deck
159 Indy @8ballr Hollow Independent Trucks
101 56mm @ojwheels Elite Mini Combo
@bronsonspeedco G3s
Black @mobgrip 🎯 
Indy 7/8ths Bolts
Fit Check: @k3vinbraun's ‘Camping Dot’ T-Shirt featuring Artwork by our friend Thomas Fernandez aka @liveradstudios 👕
🎥: @ericdanescu
#SantaCruzSkateboards

Today we are thrilled to sit down with multi talented musician, father, and skateboarder Anthony Green aka @anthonygreen666 at his music studio in Doylestown, PA. You may have heard of Anthony through his work with bands like @circasurvive, @saosinofficial, #fuckinwhatever or just his solo Anthony Green moniker. What you might not have known is that Anthony shares a deep passion for skateboarding and music and is thankful for the lessons his kids learn through those shared arts. Anthony also discusses writing new music during the pandemic, why he works on so many different projects and how stoked he is to get back on the road. For any skateboarder, musician or parent this is a must see. We can’t wait to see you on the road, Anthony! Hit our @youtube channel to watch now!
🎥: @thekillatapes @trevarcushing
🎬: @richievaldez
